OL,3,CInside Southern Water's 'super sewer'
OL,4,Ckeeping the sea off Brighton safe
OL,6,FThe regulator said five out of nine
OL,7,Fcompanies in England were rated as
OL,8,F"requiring improvement" in its annual
OL,9,Freport.
OL,11,FThere were 47 serious pollution
OL,12,Fincidents - up from 44 in 2022. Four
OL,13,Fcompanies - including Southern Water -
OL,14,Fcaused 90% of those incidents.
OL,16,FWe began our investigation, venturing
OL,17,Finto one of the oldest sewers in the
OL,18,Fcountry - the Victorian system below
OL,19,FBrighton.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/18
