OL,3,CInside Southern Water's 'super sewer'
OL,4,Ckeeping the sea off Brighton safe
OL,6,FThe super sewer cost more than #40
OL,7,Fmillion pounds and is designed to
OL,8,Fwithstand all but a one in 50 year
OL,9,Fstorm.
OL,11,FFew ever realise its there, its
OL,12,Fentrance hidden under a small kiosk on
OL,13,Fthe promenade.
OL,15,FYet, because of it, Southern Water say
OL,16,Fthey've had no sewage discharges in
OL,17,Fthe Brighton area for twelve years -
OL,18,Fdespite popular beliefs.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/18
