OL,3,CInside Southern Water's 'super sewer'
OL,4,Ckeeping the sea off Brighton safe
OL,6,FSo if it has solved the issue in this
OL,7,Farea, why not elsewhere? Why not in
OL,8,FWhitstable? Why not in Worthing?
OL,10,F"These projects are massively
OL,11,Fexpensive and they are not good for
OL,12,Fthe environment," Alex Saunders of
OL,13,FSouthern Water said.
OL,15,F"So for sure, they can play part of
OL,16,Fsolving the problems, but they're
OL,17,Fcertainly not the solution."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/18
