OL,3,CInside Southern Water's 'super sewer'
OL,4,Ckeeping the sea off Brighton safe
OL,6,FYet the sector faces a national crisis
OL,7,Fafter years of under-investment
OL,8,Fcombined with ageing infrastructure, a
OL,9,Fgrowing population and wetter
OL,10,Fconditions caused by climate change.
OL,12,FAlan Lovell, chairman of the
OL,13,FEnvironment Agency, said: "This is
OL,14,Funacceptable. The results we see are,
OL,15,Fyet again, simply not good enough."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/18
