OL,3,CInside Southern Water's 'super sewer'
OL,4,Ckeeping the sea off Brighton safe
OL,6,FSince being privatised in 1989, its
OL,7,Fthought water companies paid out more
OL,8,Fthan #70 billion in dividends - while
OL,9,Fpresiding over leakage and pollution
OL,10,Ffailures, including unknown quantities
OL,11,Fof untreated sewage pouring into
OL,12,Fcoastal waters and rivers.
OL,14,FMr Lovell said the culture within some
OL,15,Ffirms "can also perpetuate poor
OL,16,Fpractices" and warned that the
OL,17,Fregulator will not take "bad weather"
OL,18,Fas an excuse for poor environmental
OL,19,Fperformance.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/18
