OL,3,CInside Southern Water's 'super sewer'
OL,4,Ckeeping the sea off Brighton safe
OL,6,FHastings town centre was seriously
OL,7,Fflooded twice last year, after its
OL,8,Fsewers were overwhelmed.
OL,10,FBusinesses and homeowners were left
OL,11,Fcounting the cost - with Southern
OL,12,FWater under fire once again after its
OL,13,Fsystems were caught out by high tides
OL,14,Fand heavy rain.
OL,16,F60mm of rain fell in 24 hours with the
OL,17,Fdrainage overwhelmed in October - as
OL,18,Fit was in January.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/18
