OL,3,CInside Southern Water's 'super sewer'
OL,4,Ckeeping the sea off Brighton safe
OL,6,FThe company organised help for those
OL,7,Faffected, but many were left angry and
OL,8,Fupset.
OL,10,FOne newsagent told us the floods left
OL,11,Fhis business on the brink, amassing up
OL,12,Fto #50,000 in damages and lost trade.
OL,14,FFollowing repeated incidents, he can't
OL,15,Fget insured.
OL,17,F"It was up to my thighs following the
OL,18,Fmain burst, water gushed in within
OL,19,Fseconds," Dhaval Patel said.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/18
