OL,3,CInside Southern Water's 'super sewer'
OL,4,Ckeeping the sea off Brighton safe
OL,6,F"Rather than being helped, I felt
OL,7,Finsulted. It's not the value I
OL,8,Fexpected. If it happens in the future,
OL,9,FI'm doomed."
OL,11,FExperts say the lack of capacity at
OL,12,Fwastewater treatment plants means
OL,13,Fcompanies are releasing sewage into
OL,14,Fwaterways even during dry periods.
OL,16,FA study by Imperial College London
OL,17,Ffound almost 80% of sewage spills are
OL,18,Fattributable to insufficient capacity
OL,19,F- a lack of investment in
OL,20,Finfrastructure to keep up with demand.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/18
