OL,3,CInside Southern Water's 'super sewer'
OL,4,Ckeeping the sea off Brighton safe
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the Environment Agency has
OL,7,Fslashed the number of homes it expects
OL,8,Fto protect from flooding over the next
OL,9,Ffive years as higher costs have forced
OL,10,Fit to scale back.
OL,12,FA National Audit Office report said
OL,13,Fthe agency had pledged to protect
OL,14,F336,000 properties from the risk of
OL,15,Fflooding by 2027 ` but that this had
OL,16,Fbeen cut to 200,000 ` a reduction of
OL,17,F40%.
OL,19,FWe spoke to Ian Nunn from the
OL,20,FEnvironment Agency at an emergency
OL,21,Fflood depot in Rye.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/18
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
