OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1722528266
OL,3,CInside Southern Water's 'super sewer'
OL,4,Ckeeping the sea off Brighton safe
OL,6,F"What we're seeing, I think, is more
OL,7,Fsignificant rainfall events, higher
OL,8,Ftides, bigger storms. And
OL,9,Ffundamentally, we cannot protect
OL,10,Feveryone from flooding forever," he
OL,11,Ftold us.
OL,13,F"The biggest challenge is definitely
OL,14,Fclimate change. Without a doubt."
OL,16,FMr Lovell added: "We know that with a
OL,17,Fchanging climate, the country is going
OL,18,Fto experience more extreme weather
OL,19,Fpatterns, increased rainfall and more
OL,20,Frapid drought.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/18
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
