OL,3,CInside Southern Water's 'super sewer'
OL,4,Ckeeping the sea off Brighton safe
OL,6,F"Water companies must ensure that
OL,7,Fassets are resilient enough to
OL,8,Fwithstand these challenges."
OL,10,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed
OL,11,Fcalled last week's findings "shocking".
OL,13,F"For too long, water companies have
OL,14,Fpumped record levels of sewage into
OL,15,Four rivers, lakes and seas. This
OL,16,FGovernment will never let this happen
OL,17,Fagain."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/18
