OL,4,Ckeeping the sea off Brighton safe
OL,6,FThe new Government has announced plans
OL,7,Fto crack down on water firms,
OL,8,Fincluding tougher fines for pollution
OL,9,Fincidents and ensuring money is
OL,10,Finvested into infrastructure rather
OL,11,Fthan paid out in bonuses.
OL,13,FA spokesperson for Water UK, the
OL,14,Fsector's trade association, said:
OL,15,F"While results show overall water
OL,16,Fcompany environmental performance has
OL,17,Fimproved, it is clear there is more to
OL,18,Fbe done.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G15/18
