OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1722528266
OL,3,CInside Southern Water's 'super sewer'
OL,4,Ckeeping the sea off Brighton safe
OL,6,F"The performance of some companies, as
OL,7,Fthey acknowledge, is not improving
OL,8,Ffast enough and pollution incidents
OL,9,Fremain too high.
OL,11,F"Water companies have proposed
OL,12,Finvesting a record #105 billion to
OL,13,Fsecure our water supply in the future
OL,14,Fand stop sewage entering our rivers
OL,15,Fand seas.
OL,17,F"Ofwat needs to approve these plans in
OL,18,Ffull as any less will put critical
OL,19,Fimprovements at risk."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G16/18
