OL,6,FVictorian sewers, often blamed by
OL,7,Fpoliticians, were never the cause of
OL,8,Four sewage spills, experts say - the
OL,9,Fvast majority are far more modern.
OL,11,FIt's thought that less than 12 per
OL,12,Fcent of the sewage network in England
OL,13,Fand Wales was built in the 19th
OL,14,Fcentury.
OL,16,FThe majority of the network was
OL,17,Finstead built in the years before
OL,18,Fprivatisation, with approximately a
OL,19,Ffifth constructed during the 1960s and
OL,20,F1970s.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G17/18
