OL,6,FYet change is now desperately needed -
OL,7,Fand if not #40m super sewers like the
OL,8,Fone under Brighton, now estimated to
OL,9,Fcost more than #100m to build, fresh
OL,10,Fideas need to come on line, and fast.
OL,12,FYou can catch the full report on
OL,13,FSouthern Water's 'super sewer' on ITVX.
